Package wtf.choco.dragoneggdrop.particle

Class ConditionalEquationData

java.lang.Object
wtf.choco.dragoneggdrop.particle.ConditionalEquationData
public class ConditionalEquationData
extends Object
Represents a pair of equations along the x and z axis as well as a list of conditions that must be met to be used by an AnimatedParticleSession. Includes a set of data that will be used to spawn particles at any given point in an animation.
Author:
Parker Hawke - Choco
